<item>
            <title>[SPR-2161] FreeMarkerView &amp; VelocityView no longer work on servlet 2.3 containers</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2161</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Juergen,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The check to not override a content type previously set on the response that you introduced a couple of days ago in FreeMarkerView &amp;amp; VelocityView uses response.getContentType(), which is apparently servlet 2.4 specific. It throws a NoSuchMethodError on WLS 8.1sp2 ... Maybe you can code the check more defensively, or just remove it again?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="14255">SPR-2161</key>
            <summary>FreeMarkerView &amp; VelocityView no longer work on servlet 2.3 containers</summary>
