                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="18104" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Tue, 20 Jun 2006 01:09:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for pointing this out, Tom. I&apos;ve addressed this with a reflection-based check for the presence of the ServletResponse.getContentType method.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After all, we strive not just for Servlet 2.3 but also for Servlet 2.2 compatibility (except for the JSP tag libraries), so any such reports are more than welcome...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
